    <h1>There is nothing you can say</h1>
    <p>There is nothing you can say.<br>
	      Your pleading won’t stop me from<br>
       Snuffing your life today.<br></p>
    <p>As I aim my gun,<br>
	      My mind frothing and bubbling with hate,<br>
      There is nothing you can say,<br></p>
    <p>Your life for takeaway,<br>
	      But you’ll say it’s just Fate,<br>
      Snuffing your life today.<br></p>
    <p>And now, without further delay,<br>
	      I pull the trigger and terminate,<br>
      There is nothing you can say,<br></p>
    <p>Your body crumbles and decays,<br>
	        And I’m not sorry, not desolate at all,<br>
      There is nothing you can say,<br>
      Snuffing your life today.<br><br>
      ~ MØNØ<br>
      May 18th-19th, 2022</p>
